    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13695#discussion_r3453641583\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Filed <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13707\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13707</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 605772478,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1782143556
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"memo\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4dd\" role=\"img\" title=\"memo\">:memo:</span> fitzgen submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13695#pullrequestreview-4546030602\">PR review</a>.</p>",
        "id": 605780304,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1782145037
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13695#discussion_r3453796399\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I was confusing sync type vs sync ABI (that is, <code>self.types[adapter.lift.ty].async_</code> versus <code>adapter.lift.options.async_</code>). The inlining only happens for sync-to-sync ABIs but the callee's type can still be either async or sync, and replaying the deferred thread creation requires remembering this in <code>VMDeferredThread::callee_async</code>, IIUC.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 605780306,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1782145037
