    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13695#discussion_r3493380956\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Makes sense yeah, I've addressed these in <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13758\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13758</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13759\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13759</a></p>\n</blockquote>",
